p:
Kyoto Encyclopedia of Genes and Genomes (KEGG) enrichment analyses and Gene ontology (GO) analyses were performed by GOSeq Release2.12 and KOBAS v2.0 respectively
20, 21 . The terms with q-value < 0.05 were considered significantly enriched. The online database resource search tool for the retrieval of interacting Genes/Proteins (STRING, http://string-db.org/) was employed for protein–protein interaction analyses. String score higher than 700 was collected and then subjected to further analyses by Cytoscape v3.3.0 software
22 .
